data.description: This precious 3 bedroom, 2 bath house is perfect for a first time buyer and full of historic charm! Gorgeous, original doorknobs, beautiful fireplaces, and original hardwood floors. The house was redone 7 years ago, to include new windows, a new roof, and more. The HVAC was just replaced this spring. And this property even comes with the options of having solar panels. You won't want to miss looking at this one!
